                        p.
                            Fusce porta ipsum nec metus varius tincidunt. Cras luctus, felis quis fermentum pretium, velit dolor varius dui, sit amet rutrum velit arcu a turpis. Sed placerat leo et nibh consequat, vitae lacinia diam faucibus.
                            
                        .clear
                section#contact
                    .line
                    h2 Contact
                    .line
                    .break-20
                    .white-panel
                        p.big Hayley likes messages. Send her one.
                        .social
                            a(href="http://www.twitter.com/@sookiesock")
                                i.fa.fa-twitter
                            a(href="mailto:griffiths.hayley@googlemail.com")
                                i.fa.fa-envelope
        .overlay
            p Loading...              
        .portfolio-popup
            .popup-overlay
            .contents
                a.close(href="#")
                    i.fa.fa-times
                .row
                    .six.columns
                        img
                    .six.columns.description
                        h2
                        ul.skills
                        p
        script(src="//code.jquery.com/jquery-2.1.4.min.js")
        script(src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery.imagesloaded/3.1.8/imagesloaded.pkgd.min.js")
        script(src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/masonry/3.3.1/masonry.pkgd.min.js")
        script(src="site.js")
